{"title":"根据进程关键词linux批量关闭进程","date":"2023-07-28T17:40:19.037Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2023年7月28日","L":"2023/07/28","MM-DD":"07-28"},"link":"2023/07/28/根据进程关键词linux批量关闭进程","updated":"2023-07-28T09:17:16.437Z","content":"<p>少说废话，上干货</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">ps -ef|grep <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;想杀掉的进程关键字&#125;</span>|grep -v grep|awk <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#123;print &quot;kill -9 &quot;$2&#125;&#x27;</span>|sh</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#示例 关闭所有和java相关的进程</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ps -ef|grep java|grep -v grep|awk <span class=\"string\">&#x27;&#123;print &quot;kill -9 &quot;$2&#125;&#x27;</span>|sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>解析</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#列出进程</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">ps -ef</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#筛选想杀掉的进程</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep <span class=\"variable\">$&#123;想杀掉的进程关键字&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#去除这条命令所包含的关键字进程</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">grep -v grep</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#文本处理命令</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">awk </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#打印</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">print</span> </span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#杀掉进程 -9表示无条件终止，$2指代前面筛选出的进程</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"string\">&quot;kill -9 &quot;</span><span class=\"variable\">$2</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#执行命令（如果不加sh，则仅打印出要kill的进程端口，不会关掉进程）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"大数据与云计算网课答案","link":"2023/07/28/大数据与云计算网课答案"},"next":{"title":"Windows下MySQL的安装及连接开发工具","link":"2023/07/28/Windows下MySQL的安装及连接开发工具"},"plink":"http://glj520.tk/2023/07/28/根据进程关键词linux批量关闭进程/","reading_time":"180 字约 1 分钟"}